  "text": "The SVF cells were isolated from WAT of Nrf1(f)-KO and littermate control mice as described previously [CITATION_1] and cultured in DMEM with 10% FBS, 50 U/ml penicillin and 50 μg/ml streptomycin. The DMI protocol described above was used to induce adipogenesis after the cultured SVF cells became confluent. All the cells were cultured at 37°C in a 5% CO 2 environment.",
